  "task": "Edit /home/user/godot_projects/window_game/project.godot. Make exactly these changes:\n\nIn [application]:\n- config/name=\"Stellar Arena\"\n- config/icon=\"res://icon.svg\"\n\nAdd a [display] section (if missing) with:\n- window/size/viewport_width=1280\n- window/size/viewport_height=720\n- window/size/mode=2\n- window/stretch/mode=\"canvas_items\"\n\nLeave the existing [rendering] section unchanged and save the file.",
  "env": {
